graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Controller1[RayCluster Controller]
        Controller2[AppWrapper Controller]
        Webhook1[RayCluster Webhook]
        Webhook2[AppWrapper Webhook]
        CertMgr[Certificate Manager]
        Metrics[Metrics Server<br/>:8080]
        Health[Health Probe Server<br/>:8081]

        Controller1 -->|manages certs| CertMgr
        Controller2 -->|optional| CertMgr
        Webhook1 -->|uses certs| CertMgr
        Webhook2 -->|uses certs| CertMgr
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR]
    User -->|creates| AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR]

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| Controller1
    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| Controller2

    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|validates via| Webhook1
    K8sAPI -->|validates via| Webhook2

    Controller1 -->|creates| RayResources[RayCluster Resources]
    Controller1 -->|creates| Services[Services]
    Controller1 -->|creates| Routes[Routes/Ingresses]
    Controller1 -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies]
    Controller1 -->|creates| Secrets[TLS Secrets]
    Controller1 -->|creates| ServiceAccounts[ServiceAccounts]
    Controller1 -->|creates| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar]

    Controller2 -->|creates| KueueWorkload[Kueue Workload CR]
    Controller2 -->|wraps| WrappedResources[Wrapped Resources]

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]
        Kueue[Kueue]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
        ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    end

    Controller1 -->|depends on| KubeRay
    Controller2 -->|integrates| Kueue
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuth
    Services -->|cert from| ServiceCA

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| Metrics

    style Controller1 fill:#4a90e2
    style Controller2 fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook1 fill:#f5a623
    style Webhook2 fill:#f5a623
    style CertMgr fill:#7ed321
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623
    style KubeRay fill:#999
    style Kueue fill:#999
    style OAuth fill:#999
    style ServiceCA fill:#999
